column5: I haven't found anything related to that. The cooked chicken will be in a casserole.?
Nobody is going to do a "casserole search"......... You're wife made it...who knows what it is?
Well, chicken casserole was going to be a contribution to the Sunday night fish fry wehn we get up there in July. Now I'm thinking Pop Tarts as a dessert will be a better idea . PjShorthorn
